org.esigate.servlet.impl

Class ResponseCapturingWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.esigate.servlet.impl.ResponseCapturingWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse, javax.servlet.ServletResponse

    public class ResponseCapturingWrapper
extends Object
implements javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse
    Wrapper to the HttpServletResponse that intercepts the content written in order to build an HttpResponse.
    • If the content of the response is required for transformation (parseable content-type or proxy=false) or smaller than the buffer size the HttpResponse will contain the entire response
    • If the content of the response is not required for transformation, the HttpResponse will contain only an abstract of the response truncated to the bufer size. The complete response will have already been written to the original HttpServletResponse
    Author:
    Francois-Xavier Bonnet
